    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Ho-ly__ God,____ Ho-ly Might--y, Ho--ly Im--mor---tal,__ have__ mer----cy__ on___ us. \n\nHo-ly God,____ Ho-ly Might---y, Ho--ly Im--mor-----tal,__ have__ mer----cy__ on___ us. \n\nGlo--ry to the Fa----ther, and__ to the__ Son,__ and to__ the__ Ho--ly Spir----it.__\n\nBoth now__ and ev---er, and__ un--to__ the ag-----es__ of__ ag----es.__ A---men. \n\nHo---ly Im--mor---tal,__ have__ mer----cy__ on___ us. \n\nΝε ΔυναΔυ_ ναμις__________________ \n\nHo------------------ly,_____________ Ho------ly___________ Ho----ly_____ God. \n\nHo------------------ly,_____________ Ho------ly___________ Ho----ly____ Might---y.__\n\nHo------------------------------ly,___ Ho-----ly Im-mor---------tal,__ ne,________ Ho----ly__ Im--mor---tal.__\n\nHave mer------------------cy,___ have__ mer----cy__ on___ us.___________"
